---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About">
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-6">About Us</h1>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose">
        <p class="mb-4">
          Penta Yeg is a dynamic new player in the staffing industry, dedicated to providing specialized solutions for critical services like asbestos removal, water damage restoration, fire damage restoration, mold remediation, general labor, final clean up, and disinfecting and sanitation.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Our mission is simple: to connect skilled professionals with the projects that need them most, ensuring quality and integrity in every placement.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Born from the vision of five hard-working individuals, Penta Yeg started with a shared belief that staffing could be more than just filling positions—it could be about building safer, stronger communities.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          At the heart of everything we do are two guiding principles: quality and integrity. We believe that every job, no matter how tough, deserves the best talent and the highest standards.
        </p>
        <p>
          As a new company, we’re not just looking to join the industry—we’re here to redefine it. With fresh ideas and an unwavering commitment to excellence, Penta Yeg is ready to tackle the challenges of today and tomorrow.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>